2.10	Disgaea_2	Disgaea 2: Cursed Memories	Disgaea 2: Cursed Memories Makai Senki Disugaia TsÅ«, lit. "Netherworld Battle Chronicle: Disgaea 2") is a tactical role-playing game developed and published by Nippon Ichi Software for the PlayStation 2 video game console. Disgaea 2 is the sequel to 2003's Disgaea: Hour of Darkness for the PlayStation 2 and was released in Japan on February 23, 2006 and North America on August 29, 2006. It is also the predecessor to Disgaea 3: Absence of Justice for the PlayStation 3.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/77/Disgaea_2.jpg/252px-Disgaea_2.jpg
